      to stay under the 60/min aggregate rate budget.

      The test file does NOT exercise all 12 error codes â€” that's task 029's
      unit test surface. The smoke matrix exercises HAPPY PATH + the natural
      decline / empty-results / low-confidence variants that synthetic data
      produces organically.
    </step>
